==Did you know?==
*Did you know that statuephiles (or agalmatophiles, which is [[Greek]] for "statue lovers" and can also be interpreted as "[[Barbie|doll]] lovers") can also be called '''pediophiles'''? "Pedio" is from the [[Greek]] word "''paidion''", which was more often used to mean "doll" rather than "statue", but it is ultimately much the same as "[[pedo]]" (also derived from "''paidon''") and both terms are used to refer to [[children]]. Dolls were primarily children's playthings modelled after children, and for the most part still are. All of this means that "[[pedophile]]" and "pediophile" and thus "agalmatophile" are pretty much the same damned thing.

*[[Creepy|RealDolls]], BoyToys, and perhaps two other, comparatively minor brands are the only non-inflatable sex dolls that approximate the sizes of grown, physiologically [[normal]] [[women]]. These dolls cost [[Over 9000|thousands]] of [[money|dollars]], however. The highest-selling dolls cost only hundreds, and are more affordable mainly because they are '''[[loli|smaller]]''' and use [[Plastic crap|cheaper materials]]. Not surprisingly, many of these [[loli|smaller]] dolls are made in [[Japan]] and come with such options as [[Vagina|vaginal]] [[Fleshlight|sheaths]] available in what would translate to "[[Baby|infant]]" size. This doesn't help the dollfuckers and so-called statuephiles separate themselves any further from the [[pedophiles]].

*Statuephiles and dollfuckers like to bring up the [[Greek]] [[myth]] of Pygmalion. In that story, Pygmalion is an [[emo]] [[artist]] who is seemingly doomed to remain a [[virgin]] because he's [[Asperger's|awkward]], [[ugly|unattractive]], and claims he [[Gay|doesn't even like women]] until one day the statue he was sculpting is brought to life by the [[Hott|goddess]]  [[Whore|Aphrodite]]. She was well-known for having [[pity sex]] with hideous yet talented men, but decided to take a pass on Pygmalion. Pygmalion gets [[secks|laid]] and has [[children]] and lives happily ever after with a [[wife]] of his own design.

Pedophiles don't understand that this [[myth]] is really just a [[Lie|myth]], and no matter how many times they watch ''Mannequin'' it will [[never]] come true for them.

